Can't comment on the hotel restaurant as we preferred to have breakfast in the local cafe and the bar was closed during our stay.	The staff was very helpful, recommending a restaurant that turned out to be our favorite dinner spot.	The staff at the desk were excellent; they all seem to be willing to answer our questions, help us make dinner reservations, and find our way around.	The restaurant serves excellent full breakfasts, and their lunch and dinner menus are good too, if you prefer to be alone.